data.description: Charming bungalow style home on the exterior, surrounded by beautiful greenery throughout. Both sides of the 2.8 acres of yard are fenced in and extend to the back where you will find a tranquil creek, the perfect dose of nature just in your backyard! The historic barn and shed are included in the sale. When you walk into the home you will find a beautiful recently remodeled open concept with high ceilings. This area includes: new hardwood floors, paint, cabinets, counter tops, back splash, windows, trim, lighting. The kitchen will lead to the other side of the home, where it still holds its previous charm. There is plenty of room to extend the home to make it bigger! So much potential, in an amazing area close to downtown Austell!
